import React from "react";
import Layout from '../components/Layout';
import {Button, Card, Icon, Image} from "semantic-ui-react";

const UserCard = () => {
  return(
    <Layout>
        <React.Fragment>
            <Card color = "red" centered>

              <Card.Content>
                <Card.Header>
                  Anakin Skywalker
                </Card.Header>

                <Card.Meta>
                  Bio
                </Card.Meta>

                <Card.Description>
                  Has a dark side...
                </Card.Description>
              </Card.Content>
            </Card>
        </React.Fragment>
    </Layout>
  )
}


export default UserCard
